snippet.title: The Flame In The Flood
snippet.description:
The debut trailer for The Flame in the Flood, a new game from a team of AAA refugees, with veterans of places like Irrational, Harmonix, and Bungie. Now in Steam Early Access: http://store.steampowered.com/app/318600

the song is The Flame in the Flood by Chuck Ragan. Available on:

iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/flame-in-flood-feat.-fearless/id951806622?i=951806638

Amazon: http://www.amazon.com/Flame-Flood-feat-Fearless-Kin/dp/B00R8OR9KU/
